{"id":749,"date":"2025-08-18T14:26:00","date_gmt":"2025-08-18T19:26:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/?p=749"},"modified":"2025-12-18T14:35:05","modified_gmt":"2025-12-18T20:35:05","slug":"sigma-tau-gamma","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/posts\/2025\/2025\/sigma-tau-gamma\/","title":{"rendered":"Sigma Tau Gamma"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>This is part of the <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/\" data-type=\"page\" data-id=\"918\">Hazing Transparency Report<\/a>, which contains <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#terminology\">terminology definitions<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/hazing-transparency-report\/#rules\">rules defined<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull is-style-elevated is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Fall 2025<\/h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper grid-item-min-width-150 \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Incident: 8\/17\/2025<br>Location: On Campus<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Reported: 8\/18\/2025<br>Reported by: Staff, Students, Hotline Report<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">Investigation: GSU-Led<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Description<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Sigma Tau Gamma provided a common source of alcohol to underage students and new members during rush\/new member activities. New members were forced or coerced to consume alcohol and participate in drinking games leading to illness and\/or injury.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"ua_component_wrapper  \"><div class=\"ua_layout--grid\" >\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Rules Violations<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Article III.D.(3)- Alcohol<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)a. \u2013 Hazing<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.B.(2)b. \u2013 Hazing Policy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Article III.A.(4) \u2013 Published Policies<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Findings<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Found Responsible<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Date Resolved: 10\/27\/2025<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Individuals Responsible: 23<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Arrests<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>None<\/p>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div  >\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Sanctions<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Disciplinary Probation through December 15, 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Educational Assessment Fee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Campus Hazing Speaker<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Leadership Education (Executive Team, New Member, and Recruitment Leadership)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Recruitment Limitations<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of Social Privileges Fall 2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Loss of Privilege: Block Seating Fall 2025<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Required Third Party Vendor Spring 2026<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Chapter and Organizational Education (Alcohol and Hazing Prevention)<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Establishment of Harm and Risk Reduction Committee<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>International Fraternity Sanctions<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n<\/div>\n<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fall 2025 Description Sigma Tau Gamma provided a common source of alcohol to underage students and new members during rush\/new member activities. New members were forced or coerced to consume alcohol and participate in drinking games leading to illness and\/or injury.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[8],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-749","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-8"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/endhazing.sl.ua.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/749","targetHints":{"all